data.description: Great first home or investment property!  Incredible value for a 2500+ sqft home.  5 Bedroom, 2 bath (2 non-conforming) 90% finished basement, plenty of room to add garage or shop, centrally located in Rathdrum, easy access to Hwy 41 and schools, NEWLy painted exterior and interior, 2016 NEW roof, professionally cleaned, furnace serviced, easy to show, move in ready.
data.whatILove:
Property for Sale:  
3 Bed, 2 bath home. Living room, kitchen with dinning area, electric baseboard and gas heater, range, dishwasher, refrigerator, w/d hook ups, Back yard fenced, home with a covered deck.  
Partially finished Basement: It has a family room and two other rooms. 
Excellent location for access to town. 
Home sold as is.  Shown by Appointment only.
